    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving pinnacle, featuring the S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed, ensuring structural and internal longevity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback expected of this chassis. With a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline, this vehicle represents a visceral driving experience for the purist who prioritizes mechanical pedigree and performance readiness.",
