    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury crossover strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. Finished in a classic Midnight Slate, the exterior retains a deep gloss, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch reflect its life as a reliable daily driver. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced religiously every 5,000 miles; we recently replaced the brake pads and rotors to ensure peak stopping power for the next owner. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin appointed with supple charcoal leather seats that show only light softening on the driver's side bolster. All electronics, from the panoramic sunroof and dual-zone climate control to the premium 12-speaker audio system, function flawlessly. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts crisply through all gears. It\u2019s a dependable, comfortable, and stylish vehicle that is ready for its next chapter without needing any immediate mechanical investment.",
