    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm selling my trusty car and it's been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really great shape, super reliable, and has been well-cared for over the years. It's perfect for anyone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks and feels wonderful on the road. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to find a new home! Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
