      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving 3.6L M96 flat-six engine paired with a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical provenance is bolstered by a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent rear main seal service. The suspension has been optimized with Bilstein monotube dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring the chassis maintains its legendary rear-engine poise through high-load cornering. The braking system features four-piston monobloc calipers with excellent thermal capacity. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the drivetrain is internally sound and the throttle response remains sharp and linear.",
